### Configurações de Variáveis
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@auctionId = 64d1f2e3a5b6c7d8e9f01234
@userId = 123

#################################################
### RECURSOS DE LEILÃO (AUCTION)
#################################################

### Criar um Novo Leilão
# Condition: 0=New, 1=Used, 2=Refurbished
POST {{baseUrl}}/auction
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "product_name": "Macbook Pro M2",
    "category": "Electronics",
    "description": "Powerful laptop for developers with 16GB RAM and 512GB SSD.",
    "condition": 0
}

---

### Listar Leilões (Com filtros opcionais)
GET {{baseUrl}}/auction?status=0&category=Electronics&productName=Macbook
Content-Type: application/json

---

### Buscar Leilão por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/auction/{{auctionId}}
Content-Type: application/json

---

### Buscar Ganhador do Leilão
GET {{baseUrl}}/auction/winner/{{auctionId}}
Content-Type: application/json


#################################################
### RECURSOS DE LANCES (BID)
#################################################

### Criar um Novo Lance
# Lembre-se: O lance deve ser maior que o anterior e o leilão deve estar aberto
POST {{baseUrl}}/bid
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "user_id": "{{userId}}",
    "auction_id": "{{auctionId}}",
    "amount": 1500.50
}

---

### Buscar Lances de um Leilão Específico
GET {{baseUrl}}/bid/{{auctionId}}
Content-Type: application/json


#################################################
### RECURSOS DE USUÁRIO (USER)
#################################################

### Buscar Usuário por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/user/{{userId}}
Content-Type: application/json